style.technique: Blender 3D for text extrusion, vector illustration for outlines and details, cel-shaded elements in background
style.color_palette: Monochromatic white/grey for text, earthy brown for main decorative element, accented by vibrant background elements. Text: #FFFFFF, #E0E0E0, #333333. Sphere: #8B4513, #A0522D, #69341A.
style.lighting: Strong directional light from top-left, subtle rim light on text edges, soft glow behind the main sphere, soft drop shadow for depth.

composition.angle: Slight 3D tilt for main text ('NINJA JUMP'), flat front view for 'TINY'
composition.background: Stylized game scene with blurred elements, central bright glow behind the logo, decorative elements around logo (ninja character, spiked balls, platforms)
composition.depth_of_field: 3D extruded text, main sphere as a background layer, layered depth with foreground and background elements

composition.angle: 메인 텍스트('NINJA JUMP')는 약간 3D로 기울어짐, 'TINY'는 평면 정면 뷰

composition.depth_of_field: 3D 돌출(extruded) 텍스트, 메인 구체는 배경 레이어로, 전경 및 배경 요소로 레이어드된 깊이감
